description:
FOE Hair Ties - 20 Pack - No Crease Hair Ties by Just Knotted
Each package includes a variety of 20 vibrant, trendy colors. Colors may vary from those pictured.

Try the new ponytail holders that are all the rage! They are called FOE Hair Ties. You can find them in all the cute store front boutiques but not at our great price!

These fabulous elastic hair ties are great because they don't snag or damage your hair like other hair ties. They are also much stronger than traditional hair ties, so they won't break.

You'll love wearing these trendy bands as bracelets as well. Mix, match and stack them to make a fashion statement in your hair or on your wrist. Great for all hair types and all ages. 

Each elastic band is made from soft stretchy elastic fabric and hand tied with a single knot at the end. The ends are heat sealed to prevent fraying.

Colors Included:
Reds, blues, greens, oranges, yellows, white/cream, purple, black, and grays. 

Other similar colors to those pictured may be substituted as necessary.

Every FOE Hair Tie Is:
*Heat sealed to prevent fraying
*Handmade in South Carolina, USA
